<p>
  Cropping a PDF removes excess white space, scanner borders, or large margins that waste screen space — especially useful when reading on tablets or e-readers. This guide explains how to crop a PDF for free, how PDF cropping works technically, and alternative methods for Mac, Windows, and Acrobat.
</p>

